response:
Use the /v1/orders API with the CancelSubscription order action. In the processingOptions of the cancellation, configure the refund parameters.

Payload Snippet:
json
"cancelSubscription": {
    "processingOptions": {
        "runBilling": true,
        "collectPayment": false,
        "refund": true,
        "writeOff": true,
        "refundAmount": "10.00"
    }
}

Note: You cannot override the Refund Reason Code in this API call; it will use the default.
